{"tid":113991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強姦流浪狗】變態已婚男人獸交 判囚2個月","createTime":"2017-02-09T12:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T19:29:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6035262d7873c8559ca80daf5f4756329422be8","tid":113991,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170209/large/1486640321_e4e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170209%2Flarge%2F1486640321_e4e5.jpg&h=d77543e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港揭發的人獸交案件不多，被裁定罪成的案件最近一宗發生於2000年2月13日(年初九)凌晨，紅磡安靜道一個公廁內發生人獸交案件，涉事的是一頭黑色母狗，警方事後拘捕一名48歲已婚男子，並控以人獸交相關罪名。<br />\n<br />\n案件審結，中年漢承認控罪，法官判處人獸交罪成，判被告即時入獄兩個月，至於案中黑狗女本有人飼養，但事後遭主人棄養，其後再獲新主人領養，重過新生活。"},{"pid":"35a1c0bf27d2d1e9d7fa3c2d5a0cfb2777eee701","tid":113991,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"唔好再出呢單新聞喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64e4a7428e3f32eab2c6057cc1e607e19ee292e","tid":113991,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"ust南亞狗"},{"pid":"c07e008f7505296a0af75f5d1077cd3ccd8f5604","tid":113991,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"ust南亞狗"},{"pid":"2f695b03d73f06e33bab83176ae6d8379fceed8f","tid":113991,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"變態影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d291e69d0bd0d093512748168dd5d1ea95ae19d7","tid":113991,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T19:29:57.000Z","msg":"風化影<img src=\"/assets/faces/n